data.description: Opportunity knocks to capitalize on this 1955-built home. This home has plenty of potential to be transformed into a curbside beauty, or take advantage of the lot size to add an ADU, the options are there. Inside features 3 comparable bedroom sizes, galley style kitchen, breakfast area, a cozy living room, and a sprawling family room that can serve multiple purposes such as an office area, formal dining, etc. Location is prime with easy access to I-35, 183, and Airport Blvd. 15-20 commute to Austin Bergstrom, about 10 min to UT and downtown Austin, and just minutes to the Mueller area!
